::Kaiser::
       He mumbles to himself as his thrusts are blocked and blocks the upward 
slash with his blades crossed above his opponent's.  He then spins himself 
over his opponent's blade and drops to a crouch.  He lashes out with his 
nearest leg in a sweep to knock the legs out from under DeathSteel.
